text: Abhinav Tandel (born 23 September 1998) is an Indian cricketer. He made his List A debut for Gujarat in the 2017–18 Vijay Hazare Trophy on 12 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Indian cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Gujarat cricketers
